# Authors and Contributors

## Magic Terminal Project

### Primary Author
- Wang Yiyang <wangyiyang@example.com> - Project maintainer and lead developer

### Magic Terminal Features and Enhancements
- Cross-platform build system and CI/CD pipeline
- macOS DMG packaging
- Enhanced documentation (Chinese and English)
- Project restructuring and modernization
- Release automation scripts

## Original fyne-io/terminal Project

Magic Terminal is based on the fyne-io/terminal project. We gratefully acknowledge
the original authors and contributors:

### Original Authors
- The Fyne.io development team
- All contributors to the fyne-io/terminal project

### Original Project
- Repository: https://github.com/fyne-io/terminal
- License: BSD 3-Clause License

## Acknowledgments

We thank the Fyne.io team and the open source community for creating the 
foundation upon which Magic Terminal is built. The original terminal emulator
provided an excellent starting point for this enhanced version.

## Contributing

Contributions to Magic Terminal are welcome! Please see CONTRIBUTING.md for
guidelines on how to contribute to this project.

---

For a complete list of contributors, see the Git commit history:
```
git log --format='%aN <%aE>' | sort -u
```
